text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to stop safari from filling in the address bar on an iphone?
text.Response A: Sure, I can help you with that.  Is there a way you can change the settings on your phone so that it doesn’t fill in the address bar?
text.Response B:
Open your iPhone's Settings.
Scroll down and tap Safari.
Slide the "Preload Top Hit" button to the Off position.

655.displayed_text:
Prompt

Can you tell me how to stop safari from filling in the address bar on an iphone?

Response A

Sure, I can help you with that. Is there a way you can change the settings on your phone so that it doesn’t fill in the address bar?

Response B

Open your iPhone's Settings.
Scroll down and tap Safari.
Slide the "Preload Top Hit" button to the Off position.
